					<div class="jeg_block_heading jeg_block_heading_4 jeg_subcat_right">
                     <h3 class="jeg_block_title"><span>IN THE CURRENT</span></h3>
                     
                 </div>
					<div class="jeg_block_container">
                    
                    <div class="jeg_posts jeg_load_more_flag"><article class="jeg_post jeg_pl_lg_3 format-standard">
                    <div class="jeg_thumb">
                        
                        <a href="https://safety4sea.com/accelleron-finding-the-fuels-to-save-shippings-decarbonization-goals/" aria-label="Read article: Accelleron: Finding the fuels to save shipping’s decarbonization goals"><div class="thumbnail-container  size-715 "><img decoding="async" width="350" height="250" src="https://safety4sea.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/accelleron-net-zero-form-2880x1920-1-350x250.jpeg" class=" wp-post-image" alt="accelleron" /></div></a>
                        <div class="jeg_post_category">
                            <span><a href="https://safety4sea.com/category/green/green-shipping/" class="category-green-shipping">Green Shipping</a></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="jeg_postblock_content">
                        <h3 class="jeg_post_title">
                            <a href="https://safety4sea.com/accelleron-finding-the-fuels-to-save-shippings-decarbonization-goals/">Accelleron: Finding the fuels to save shipping’s decarbonization goals</a>
                        </h3>
                        <div class="jeg_post_meta"><div class="jeg_meta_author coauthor"><span class="meta_text by">by</span><a href="https://safety4sea.com/author/ap/">The Editorial Team</a></div><div class="jeg_meta_date"><a href="https://safety4sea.com/accelleron-finding-the-fuels-to-save-shippings-decarbonization-goals/"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> December 1, 2025</a></div></div>
                        <div class="jeg_post_excerpt">
                            <p>The technology for net zero shipping is ready, but the fuels are not. A new Accelleron report calls for a cross-sector push to accelerate carbon-neutral fuel development and keep climate ambitions on course.</p>
                            <a href="https://safety4sea.com/accelleron-finding-the-fuels-to-save-shippings-decarbonization-goals/" class="jeg_readmore">Read more<span class="screen-reader-text">Details</span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article><article class="jeg_post jeg_pl_lg_3 format-standard">
                    <div class="jeg_thumb">
                        
                        <a href="https://safety4sea.com/modular-turbocharger-design-prepares-shipowners-for-future-demands/" aria-label="Read article: Modular turbocharger design prepares shipowners for future demands"><div class="thumbnail-container  size-715 "><img decoding="async" width="350" height="250" src="https://safety4sea.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ACCX300-L_Hero-image_build10_Wide_Final-350x250.jpg" class=" wp-post-image" alt="turbocharger" /></div></a>
                        <div class="jeg_post_category">
                            <span><a href="https://safety4sea.com/category/green/technology/" class="category-technology">Technology</a></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="jeg_postblock_content">
                        <h3 class="jeg_post_title">
                            <a href="https://safety4sea.com/modular-turbocharger-design-prepares-shipowners-for-future-demands/">Modular turbocharger design prepares shipowners for future demands</a>
                        </h3>
                        <div class="jeg_post_meta"><div class="jeg_meta_author coauthor"><span class="meta_text by">by</span><a href="https://safety4sea.com/author/ap/">The Editorial Team</a></div><div class="jeg_meta_date"><a href="https://safety4sea.com/modular-turbocharger-design-prepares-shipowners-for-future-demands/"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> December 1, 2025</a></div></div>
                        <div class="jeg_post_excerpt">
                            <p>Accelleron’s new ACCX300-L turbocharger series provides shipowners with a modular platform designed for greater energy efficiency, ease of servicing and the migration to carbon-neutral fuels.</p>
                            <a href="https://safety4sea.com/modular-turbocharger-design-prepares-shipowners-for-future-demands/" class="jeg_readmore">Read more<span class="screen-reader-text">Details</span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article></div>
