                    <div class="jeg_inner_post">
                        <div class="jeg_thumb">
                            
                            <a href="https://safety4sea.com/cm-safety4sea-esg-barometer-survey-2026-what-is-truly-driving-maritime-esg-today/" aria-label="Read article: SAFETY4SEA ESG Barometer Survey 2026: What is truly driving maritime ESG today?"><div class="thumbnail-container  size-500 "><img decoding="async" width="750" height="375" src="https://safety4sea.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/ESG-Barometer-Survey-880x440-2025_03-01-750x375.jpg" class=" wp-post-image" alt="" /></div></a>
